For SHA-1 certificate fingerprint, just use the `keytool` command. In my case, my `debug.keystore` was located at my root project folder at `.android/debug.keystore` after running `flutter run`

My supabase google clientid uses the web client id created in Google Cloud console.

My Flutter version is `3.24.4` at the time of writing.

Hope this helps anyone who are still facing this issue!

